erence/Global_Objects/Intl/PluralRules\"><code>Intl.PluralRules</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Segmenter\"><code>Intl.Segmenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format</code></strong> Eigenschaft gibt eine Getterfunktion zurück, die eine Zahl nach den Sprach- und Formatierungsoptionen dieses&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>NumberFormat</code></a> Objektes formatiert.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/intl-numberformat-prototype-format.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>numberFormat</var>.format(<var>number</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"number\"><code>number</code></dt>\n <dd>Zahl, die formatiert werden soll.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die Funktion, die von <code>format</code> Getter zurückgegeben wird, formatiert eine Zahl in einen String nach den angegebenen Sprach- und Formatierungsoptionen des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>NumberFormat</code></a> Objektes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_von_format","title":"Einsatz von <code>format</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Einsatz der vom <code>format</code> Getter zurückgegebenen Funktion zum Formatieren eines Währungswertes, hier für Russland:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">style</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'currency'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">currency</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'RUB'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> numberFormat <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ru-RU'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>numberFormat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">654321.987</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// → \"654 321,99 руб.\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz von format"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_format_mit_map","title":"Einsatz <code>format</code> mit <code>map</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Einsatz der vom <code>format</code> Getter zurückgegebenen Funktion zum Formatieren von allen Zahlen in einem Array. Zu bemerken ist, dass die Funktion an das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>NumberFormat</code></a> Objekt gebunden ist, von dem sie stammt, so dass es direkt in <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/map\"><code>Array.prototype.map</code></a> verwendet werden kann.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">123456.789</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">987654.321</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">456789.123</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> numberFormat <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NumberFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'es-ES'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formatted <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>numberFormat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>format<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>formatted<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'; '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// → \"123.456,789; 987.654,321; 456.789,123\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz format mit map"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/1.0/#sec-11.3.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 1.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/2.0/#sec-11.3.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 2.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma402/#sec-Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Intl.NumberFormat.format","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat/format/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/toLocaleString\"><code>Number.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format Eigenschaft gibt eine Getterfunktion zurück, die eine Zahl nach den Sprach- und Formatierungsoptionen dieses NumberFormat Objektes formatiert.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Intl.NumberFormat.prototype.format","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/numberformat/format","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/numberformat/format/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Glob